TITLE: Posts Table Schema Definition in MySQL
DESCRIPTION: The table schema for the Posts table showing its structure and the available indexes, including the single-column and multi-column indexes relevant to the query optimization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/mattermost-developer-documentation/blob/master/site/content/blog/2020-11-17-mysql-index-merge.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

