TITLE: C Functions for io_uring Request Handling
DESCRIPTION: C functions using liburing to push read and write requests to the submission queue and handle completions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mattermost/mattermost-developer-documentation/blob/master/site/content/blog/2020-05-20-hands-on-iouring-go.md#2025-04-23_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: c
CODE:
```
int push_read_request(int file_fd, off_t file_sz) {
    struct file_info *fi;
    struct io_uring_sqe *sqe = io_uring_get_sqe(&ring);
    io_uring_prep_readv(sqe, file_fd, fi->iovecs, total_blocks, 0);
    io_uring_sqe_set_data(sqe, fi);
    return 0;
}

int push_write_request(int file_fd, void *data, off_t file_sz) {
    struct file_info *fi;
    struct io_uring_sqe *sqe = io_uring_get_sqe(&ring);
    io_uring_prep_writev(sqe, file_fd, fi->iovecs, 1, 0);
    io_uring_sqe_set_data(sqe, fi);
    return 0;
}
```

